8}, {\"ngram\": \"industrial facilities\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5421}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed-use campuses\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We create state-of-the-art life science centers through our Breakthrough Properties joint venture, and foster innovation through our strategic proptech investments.\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-art\", \"from\": 5466, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"our Breakthrough Properties joint venture\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5544}, {\"ngram\": \"foster innovation\", \"from\": 5550, \"to\": 5567}, {\"ngram\": \"our strategic proptech investments\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With global vision, on-the-ground expertise and a personalized approach, we are unparalleled in our ability to foster innovation, quickly adapt to global and local trends and proactively anticipate our customers' evolving needs.\", \"from\": 5612, \"to\": 5840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"global vision\", \"from\": 5617, \"to\": 5630}, {\"ngram\": \"the-ground\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5645}, {\"ngram\": \"a personalized approach\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5683}, {\"ngram\": \"our ability\", \"from\": 5708, \"to\": 5719}, {\"ngram\": \"innovation\", \"from\": 5730, \"to\": 5740}, {\"ngram\": \"global and local trends\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5782}, {\"ngram\": \"our customers' evolving needs\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By focusing on health and wellness, enlightened placemaking and customer-focused initiatives such as our tenant amenities platform, ZO, and our flexible space and co-working brand, Studio, we tend not just to our physical buildings, but to the people who inhabit them on a daily basis.\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 6126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5862}, {\"ngram\": \"wellness\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5875}, {\"ngram\": \"placemaking and customer-focu